  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7838419/" class="title-link">要多么无耻的时代，才能出现这样无耻的著作</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7838419"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2164580-3.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2164580/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">tradition</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar20 main-title-rating" title="较差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-04-03"
      class="main-meta">2016-04-03 19:31:01</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7838419_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  姚出版本书的评“自古得天下之正莫如我朝”及续两篇文章，基本就是一个精神病患者的意淫东西，毫无史实价值可言，这种垃圾也能算学术？简直笑话  比如说康熙认为南明史不应该包含在明史中，被姚认为是毁灭华夏历史的关键所在，但编著石匮书的大明遗民张岱也不主张南明史列入明...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7838419/#comments">(22回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">16有用 / 24没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7838419_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7838419_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
